name: Parrot
tagline: A model based web framework base on Bootstrap and ReactJS
body:
### Welcome to Parrot project
Parrot is a model based web framework.  
Base on ReactJS and Bootstrap.

### Authors and Contributors
In 2014, @bradwoo8621 founded NEST. Meanwhile, Parrot and others projects were created.  
This Project is forked from [bradwoo8621/parrot](https://github.com/bradwoo8621/parrot)

### Guide of Parrot
Visit [Development Guide](http://ebaotech.github.io/parrot/guide/index.html)
